-- Aegon Names Douglas Henck Chief Executive of Reorganized Asian Businesses
-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 2010-12-07T21:48:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-07/aegon-names-douglas-henck-chief-executive-of-reorganized-asian-businesses.html
Aegon NV , the Dutch insurer and owner
of Transamerica Corp., named  Douglas Henck  as chief executive
officer of Asian businesses.  Aegon will reorganize its operations in the region under a
headquarters in Hong Kong, the firm said today in a statement
distributed by PR Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Andrew Frye  in New York at 
 afrye@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net . 